{"title":"线坠——工地所见","authors":["弘征"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":3,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"线坠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——工地所见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弘征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一块铅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻柔、沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默不言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如是一块铝呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锃亮得能照见人的笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果一朝电化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人将称赞你金灿灿的容颜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁都知道你的重量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿让手去拈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有毅力无限延伸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不是一团泥可随心去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捏造型成一个圆锥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是使命决定的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正适合你的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如是一个圆珠多好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手掌中轻快地飞旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在正砌着的高墙顶端"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂下一根细长的线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用得着你校正大厦的偏差"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着记录你的功业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落成的日子彩旗飞舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新饰的霓虹灯正傲云天……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}